\b \cf0 Description:
\b0 \
\
- impossible to supply an inline comment for a line which only has a label. For instance:\
\
280 OSRC ;OPEN SCREEN ROUTINE\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
\cf0 This will generate an error six.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\b \cf0 Solution:
\b0 \
\
280 OSRC NOP ;OPEN SCREEN ROUTINE\
\
else\
\
280 OSRC .OPT LIST ;OPEN SCREEN ROUTINE\
\

